attributionInfo.agentName: Abby Stevenson, Ed Guzman and Tyler Buske

data.description: $15k of equity updated two story home featuring high ceilings with an open floor plan. Wood flooring throughout first floor with enclosed office space. Kitchen has granite countertops, white cabinets, travertine stone tile for backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. **Fridge & dishwasher are included** Primary bedroom has walk-in closet, its own bathroom with double vanity sink, soaking garden tub and separate walk-in shower. Second bathroom also has double vanity sink and tub/shower combo. **Water softener is included and has been paid off** Garage has a full epoxy floor **Organizing fixtures in garage are included** Backyard covered patio consists of a level clement slab with two pergolas. Sprinkler irrigation system with 5 water zones throughout front and backyard. Walking distance to neighborhood pool and amenities. San Geronimo Air Park is nextdoor to the neighborhood with a view of the landing strip from the front porch.
